I will say that there's no reason it should affect OG to steep at low volume. Steeping grains in general only add a very low number of ppgYeah, you have the thrust of it there. Hop utilization is similar to tannins in that higher pH will extract it better, but its actually desirable. So yes, top water up for the boil, then top up again at the end.
